@cbaptista Also, please ensure you are using a valid `--ws-url` and a valid `--log-format`. e.g.,

    goaccess -f pound.log -o /var/www/html/report.html --real-time-html --ws-url=your_server_ip_where_goaccess_is_running --log-format VCOMBINED

Feel free to post a few lines from your access log to verify the log format. Also, port 7890 must be open.
